    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013420/extras/25d170c49eebd67b85273445b60a98f0.avif?t=1766305557\" width=905 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For hundreds of years, circles of druids have been tasked with leading the spirits of the dead to the spiritual world.    <br>Suddenly, 40 days after the death of a powerful druid, Elara, a mysterious beast of roots and dirt appeared. The beast seemingly aimed to destroy the forest and its inhabitants.   <br>Elara's husband, another powerful druid, Arik, is the only one who can, together with the forest creatures, stop the beast and put all souls to rest.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Move by using animal abilities inside your amulet – the frog, the raven and the fox</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013420/extras/23f9b5aff8f15567620f4ffc1cc4af58.poster.avif?t=1766305557\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013420/extras/23f9b5aff8f15567620f4ffc1cc4af58.webm?t=1766305557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013420/extras/23f9b5aff8f15567620f4ffc1cc4af58.mp4?t=1766305557\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Meet different animals and their ruined lands</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013420/extras/785a3beda86e994e211b4e424b73baaa.poster.avif?t=1766305557\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013420/extras/785a3beda86e994e211b4e424b73baaa.webm?t=1766305557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013420/extras/785a3beda86e994e211b4e424b73baaa.mp4?t=1766305557\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collect Elara's amulet shards</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013420/extras/62361ca16f4588760690001da4d6ad9f.poster.avif?t=1766305557\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013420/extras/62361ca16f4588760690001da4d6ad9f.webm?t=1766305557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013420/extras/62361ca16f4588760690001da4d6ad9f.mp4?t=1766305557\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The story</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Oprost is a journey of grief through a precision platformer that uses power of animal moves instead of classic jumping. Help Arik, a druid who recently lost his wife, in battling his grief as well as the beast of thorns and weeds who is destroying his forest.</p>",
